Bash command to fix filenames (from "Render (0).png" to "render0.png"):
    count=0; for i in ./* ; do mv "$i" "render$count.png" ; ((count++)) ; done

To build
```
$ bundle exec jekyll build --verbose
```

To run
```
$ bundle exec jekyll serve
```

To update gems/dependencies
```
$ bundle update
$ bundle install
```

